{"tid":1103284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣80歲老翁上吊亡","createTime":"2019-04-12T09:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T10:00:57.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db183058994f025cb18dc781a45e7cd72338f709","tid":1103284,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555054020_1012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555054020_1012.jpg&h=073d5585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老翁上吊昏迷送院搶救。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣希雲街11號禮希大樓，下午2時43分，一名女子發現其年約80歲丈夫，在單位內上吊，報警求助，救援人員到場前事主已被解下，昏迷不醒，由兩名女親友陪同送院搶救，惜最終不治。警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=c9a3b85b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190412/59480321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480321&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=12ef46d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480321&h=38cc3169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190412/59480321</a>"},{"pid":"84e04a5ea85d309658f433dee7ffaf295bc79a2c","tid":1103284,"uid":242064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01f185ae39e8c20e4384d6c